@host = https://localhost:5001
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@version = 1

### Get order (check ETag in response)
GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}

###

### Update with correct version
PATCH {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "{{version}}"

{
  "status": "Cancelled"
}

###

### Update with wrong version (412)
PATCH {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "999"

{
  "status": "Cancelled"
}